ame":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774690549696,"sessionId":"62c4b07b-ad90-45e1-a319-9e0e0f94680a","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44794,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/62c4b07b-ad90-45e1-a319-9e0e0f94680a.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个定时任务，需要我先检测当前是否有活跃对话。让我查询 sessions_list 来检查。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u3eerxzlrxmt_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774690550213}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774690555453}}
{"type":"message","id":"e222cfdf","parentId":"b567546a","timestamp":"2026-03-28T09:35:59.111Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从结果来看，只有一个session，而且是当前这个cron任务本身。没有其他用户活跃对话。所以应该执行自主学习。\n\n我需要：\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n让我先用 web search skill 来搜索这些行业的最新动态。","thinkingSignature":"3b4bc43c6bd04421592049b31ee7d61444ede3b8eb90c3508759d9103ba0fdaa"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wi5vc3aos8h7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":830,"output":138,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44949,"cost":{"input":0.000249,"output":0.0001656,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00173403}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774690555456}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8391d14","parentId":"e222cfdf","timestamp":"2026-03-28T09:35:59.117Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wi5vc3aos8h7_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774690559114}}
{"type":"message","id":"491f8c5b","parentId":"e8391d14","timestamp":"2026-03-28T09:36:03.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要使用 miaoda-studio-cli search-summary 来搜索行业最新动态。让我搜索几个关键词：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态\n2. 智能安防行业最新动态\n3. 网络系统集成最新动态\n4. IT运维服务最新动态\n\n我可以并行搜索这些关键词。","thinkingSignature":"7bf0a1ccba1f92f07ac2af38923601ee7b28fc54fc7d726c803e218074a1f175"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vhf0dgd6gp7s_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年最新动态 政策\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vhf0dgd6gp7s_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业 2026年最新动态 趋势\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vhf0dgd6gp7s_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026最新动态\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1483,"output":214,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45678,"cost":{"input":0.00044489999999999997,"output":0.0002568,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00202113}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774690559117}}
